Content: Are you looking for a switch only clan? Then Team Agent is the clan for you! We hope to be a friendly environment for less competitive players and a helpful environment for some of the better switch players out there. We feel as if Switch players are looked down upon. Our goal is to prove everyone wrong. If you're a switch player and want to join_ DM me.NL-Switch Platform OnlyNL- Mic needed to talk on discord or fortnite game chatNL-Speak EnglishNL- NAE serversNL- Don’t be toxicNL- Be matureNL-Have funNL-Be active on discordNL[-Free Agents Wanted-]NL[-Casual team-] NL    50 wins NL     0.5 kdNLNL[-Competitive-] NL    150 wins NL2.5% win ratioNLAt Least  2 KDNL                                                          Also_ you can submit clips to us in our server and we'll put it into a montage!NL                 Again_ Please DM me if you’re interested
